The management of Dangote Cement has extended its ongoing sales promo by additional four weeks to enable its customers win the outstanding 20 cars and other prizes. The Group Managing Director (GMD) of Dangote Cement, Eng. Joseph Makoju, who revealed this during another car presentation in Lokoja, Kogi State, said, “We are excited to inform you that we have decided to extend the ongoing National Consumer Promotion tagged: “Dangote Bag of Goodies”. Engr. Makoju said while the promotion would now end on October 15, customers still had till October 31, 2019, to redeem their respective prizes. OVER 5,000 NIGERIAN MEN HAVE  OVERCOME POOR BEDROOM PERFORMANCE SYNDROME DUE TO THIS BRILLIANT DISCOVERY He said, “Based on the above dates, packaging of cement in the special promo bags with scratch card insertion will continue till October 15, while lucky consumers will be able to continue redeeming their prizes up until October 31, 2019” The National Sales Director of Dangote Cement, Adeyemi Fajobi, said over 21 million winners of various items were expected to emerge at the end of the promotion Dangote Cement Marketing Director, Mrs. Funmi Sanni, urged the people to continue to buy Dangote Cement as consumers would win 43 cars, 24 tricycles, 24 motorcycles, 550 refrigerators, 400 television sets, 300,000 Dangote foods goodies packs and recharge cards for all networks worth N200,000,000.00. 500 persons receive prizes from Dangote Cement Dangote Promo: Bricklayer, artisan win cars in Ijebu-ode, Ikorodu Dangote Cement promo: Winners emerge in Edo, Osogbo, others